<h2><strong>### Purchases during the event (some food run out)</strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-family: 'courier new', courier;">|                | Quantity | Cost (rounded) |</span><br /><span style="font-family: 'courier new', courier;">| ----:          | :------- | :--- |</span><br /><span style="font-family: 'courier new', courier;">| Watermelon     | 1        | 7.00 |</span><br /><span style="font-family: 'courier new', courier;">| Hot dog buns   | 12       | 4.00 |</span><br /><span style="font-family: 'courier new', courier;">| Hamburger buns | 24       | 8.00 |</span></p>
<h2><strong>## Preparations</strong></h2>
<p>* Canadian tire has propane<br />* Bring out grill and get it started<br />* Put food and drinks out on tables</p>
<h1><strong>## Event</strong></h1>
<p>* We had about 50-70 people come overall<br />* People came in 2 waves: one at noon and one around 1:30<br />* Some people wanted relish<br />* People seemed to have fun!</p>
<h1><strong>## Recommendations</strong></h1>
<p>* Most of the food was eaten. We had way too many buns left over.<br />* Buy sweet relish<br />* Send out an email at the time of the event saying it's happening now<br />* Start cooking at least 30 minutes early! It takes a while to get the grill<br /> hot and the first batch of food ready. This means start setup an hour<br /> before the BBQ.<br />* Buy more veggie burgers! 4 people responded to the questionaire asking<br /> for vegetarian option, I bought 16 but that wasn't nearly enough and<br /> you couldn't get veggie burgers on campus.<br />* Just avoid pork products (hot dogs and sausages). So many <br /> people don't eat pork.<br />* Nestors used to sell veggie burgers but they no longer appear to do so.<br /> I couldn't find any at Walmart either. I ended up buying them at Donald's<br /> market at Hastings and Nanaimo.<br />* Music might be nice...<br />* Only TTW likes root beer and no one liked coke zero<br />* Walmart in Lougheed has grocery items<br />* get someone with a car to commit to help as <br /> renting a car to get propane is expensive</p> <div class="attachmentsContainer">

